members.name: SourceBufferList.length
members.description: Returns the number of SourceBuffer objects in the list.

members.name: SourceBufferList.SourceBuffer()
members.description: This getter allows the SourceBuffer objects in the list to be accessed with an array operator (i.e. [].)

parameters.name: index
parameters.description: The index position of the SourceBuffer object you want to return.
